METAL PACKAGES INDUSTRIES
TECHNICAL DATA SHEET: FOOD & INDUSTRIAL ALUMINIUM COLLAPSIBLE TUBES

1. PRODUCT DESCRIPTION
Heavy-duty, high-barrier aluminium collapsible tubes designed for food pastes and aggressive industrial chemicals, adhesives, sealants, silicones, and lubricants.

2. SPECIFICATIONS & DIMENSIONS
- Diameter Range: 19.0 mm to 45.0 mm
- Wall Thickness: 0.15 mm - 0.22 mm
- Capacity: 15 ml to 200 ml
- Purity: 99.7% pure refined aluminium slugs
- Barrier Properties: Complete barrier against light, oxygen, moisture, and odors

3. LINERS & COATINGS
- Internal Lacquer: Specialized chemical-resistant epoxy coating or food-grade lacquer
- Base Coat: Standard white or grey protective base coat
- Sealant: High-performance end-band latexing for leak prevention of low-viscosity materials

4. APPLICATIONS
- Food Pastes (Spread, Tomato paste, Garlic paste)
- Industrial Adhesives (Epoxy glue, Rubber cement, Cyanoacrylate)
- Silicone Sealants & Caulks
- Grease, Oils, and Mechanical Lubricants
- Artists Paint & Watercolors

5. MECHANICAL PERFORMANCE
- Burst pressure tested for high security
- High elasticity of aluminium wall for smooth product extrusion

